description.en:
Multi-Reflectionary Coin on the Binance Smart Chain.
100% Community Owned
Crypto Puffs has no pre-sale, no team tokens, no venture capitalists and no key opinion leaders. General Shills is commited to fair launching crypto cereals. Our aim is to build strong and sustainable communities.
